=== Noun Phrase ===
'''bat shit''' 

# Fecal matter or solid waste produced by bats. See [[w:Bat|Wikipedia:Bat]]. Deposits of bat shit are commonly found in caves, and often in barn lofts where bats live.

# To become excessively upset or agitated. ''Going bat shit''.

